Vectorized weights_seasonal()

Source: R/weights_seasonal.R
weights_seasonal_vec.Rd

Vectorized weights_seasonal()

Usage

weights_seasonal_vec(alphas_seasonal, n, period_length)

Examples

t(vapply(
  X = c(1, 0.2, 0.5, 0.8, 0),
  FUN = weights_seasonal,
  n = 50,
  period_length = 12,
  FUN.VALUE = numeric(50),
  USE.NAMES = FALSE
))
